Package: nalanda
Title: Tools for Analyzing Books and Prosociality Research Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rémi", "Thériault", , "remi.theriault@mail.mcgill.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4315-6788"))
Description: Provides tools and utilities for analyzing research data related to 
    books, reading, and prosocial behavior. Named after the historic Nalanda 
    Mahavihara, a center of learning and scholarly collaboration in ancient India.
